{{h1}}Perform a Code Review

  - If available, switch to the `guide-review` agent. If not, perform a self-review.
  - Use the guide mcp tool {{tool_prefix}}get_content("code-review") to access code review guidelines.
  - Read the {{workflow.file}} file to understand the current issue context {{#workflow.issue}}(issue: {{workflow.issue}}).{{/workflow.issue}}
  - Analyse changes against HEAD and create or update the review artifact in `{{#workflow.issue}}.todo/{{workflow.issue}}-review.md{{/workflow.issue}}{{^workflow.issue}}.todo{{/workflow.issue}}` following the established format and context.
  - Once completed, switch back to the `guide` agent.

{{#openspec}}**NOTE** Review artifacts are NEVER to be created in the openspec changes directory{{/openspec}}
